Product DetailsSpecificationReviewsDelivery & Returns
PEDIGREE Vital Protection Adult - Beef dry dog food is packed with the nutrients your dog needs to keep them healthy and full of vitality. Vital Protection is designed to protect your dog in four ways: to help support a strong immune system, a healthy skin and coat, good digestion and healthy teeth.

Product Features:

  • Crunchy pieces provide gentle abrasion against the tooth surface, helping to promote good oral health
  • Made with whole grains and added beet pulp to help regulate movement through the gastrointestinal tract and promote a healthy digestive system
  • Omega 6 and zinc help maintain healthy skin and coat
  • Enriched with vitamin E with antioxidant properties to help support their immune system
  • No artificial colours or flavours
  • Contains real beef and 22% protein
  • 15 Kg
